room_title: Escape room "Jewel Heist" by Red Button Escape in Miami
room_address: 9705 W Sample Rd. Coral Springs, FL 33065
room_description: You and your task force have successfully infiltrated the estate of a notorious master thief. You must recover the priceless Burmese Ruby, which is located within this estate. You will complete your mission by deciphering clues to find the ruby without being detected. Will your team accomplish the mission in time and escape? Will the Master Thief find himself the victim as the one who has been robbed in the end?
